{"title":"Hexo Instructions","uid":"f984699155b83aa2788288ed319191b9","slug":"Hexo-Instructions","date":"2022-12-02T14:24:59.000Z","updated":"2022-12-05T13:02:45.993Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo-Instructions.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://miro.medium.com/max/1200/1*zGn8GFhpCNdbO3wSvJO2JQ.jpeg","content":"<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><p>Create a new post</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo new &quot;My New Post&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<p>Create a draft which will not be published</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo new draft &quot;My New Draft&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can simply use <code>hexo new &#39;title&#39;</code> to create a new file.</p>\n<p>The default type of this file can be changed in <code>_config.yml</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"># Writing\nnew_post_name: :title.md # File name of new posts\ndefault_layout: draft</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"Tag-Plugins\"><a href=\"#Tag-Plugins\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tag Plugins\"></a>Tag Plugins</h2><p><a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/tag-plugins\">Documentation</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Code-Block\"><a href=\"#Code-Block\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Code Block\"></a>Code Block</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-start=\"1\" data-line=\"\" data-line-offset=\"0\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">alert(&quot;Hello World!&quot;);\nvar a &#x3D; &quot;hello&quot;;</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>python</span></div><code class=\"language-python\">def hello():\n    print(&quot;Hello World!&quot;)</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"Blockquote\"><a href=\"#Blockquote